  "detailed_description": "A 90’s nostalgia inspired lo-fi adventure with a relaxing atmosphere and wholesome story, paced between tiny planet platforming and puzzle-solving.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800390/extras/10e18ea488b44b7dc40c8559ddea2e19.avif?t=1762192315\" width=420 height=69 /></span><br><br>In Astro Pig you play as Buyk, a piglet space cadet, on a mysterious mission through uncharted territory together with his intelligent ship – talk with the galaxy sector's inhabitants, solve challenges to open up new paths and help him find what he's looking for.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800390/extras/920a4c38f7222a022fcc06be5507763b.poster.avif?t=1762192315\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800390/extras/920a4c38f7222a022fcc06be5507763b.webm?t=1762192315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800390/extras/920a4c38f7222a022fcc06be5507763b.mp4?t=1762192315\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800390/extras/b0f9872d60594fd89ab60574f330e95a.avif?t=1762192315\" width=420 height=69 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Explore <strong>three different worlds</strong> with <strong>dozens of stages</strong> and many <strong>puzzle mechanics</strong>;<br></li><li> <strong>Talk</strong> with many different <strong>NPCs</strong> in a lighthearted, quirky dialogue style;<br></li><li> Unlock <strong>three retro addictive minigames</strong> for your handheld console;<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800390/extras/94c1b454d6800b61aeddb7517117f4e5.poster.avif?t=1762192315\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800390/extras/94c1b454d6800b61aeddb7517117f4e5.webm?t=1762192315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800390/extras/94c1b454d6800b61aeddb7517117f4e5.mp4?t=1762192315\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> Get <strong>Steam Achievements</strong>;<br></li><li> Listen to <strong>over 40 completely original lo-fi tracks</strong>;<br></li><li> And <strong>make your own tracks</strong> with our <strong>Make-a-Beat</strong> system!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800390/extras/09a0bba7059267c2a0d91efa71295c42.poster.avif?t=1762192315\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800390/extras/09a0bba7059267c2a0d91efa71295c42.webm?t=1762192315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800390/extras/09a0bba7059267c2a0d91efa71295c42.mp4?t=1762192315\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
